text: "Suicide Blonde" is the lead single by Australian rock new wave band INXS and taken from their seventh studio album X. It went to number 1 in Canada and New Zealand, number 2 in Australia, number 3 in Ireland, number 9 in the United States and number 11 in the United Kingdom. ==Track listings== 7-inch and cassette single # "Suicide Blonde" – 3:55 # "Everybody Wants U Tonight" – 5:08 UK CD single # "Suicide Blonde" (7-inch version) # "Suicide Blonde" (Demolition mix) # "Everybody Wants U Tonight" # "Suicide Blonde" (7-inch Nik mix) US maxi-CD single # "Suicide Blonde" (7-inch mix) – 3:54 # "Suicide Blonde" (Earth mix) – 5:39 # "Suicide Blonde" (Devastation mix) – 6:19 # "Suicide Blonde" (Milk mix) – 5:40 # "Suicide Blonde" (Demolition mix) – 6:53 # "Everybody Wants U Tonight" – 5:09 == References == Category:1990 songs Category:INXS songs
